overview.en: Metasens is the metaverse project rolled out by Imperium Technology Group in 2021 Q4. It aims to provide an open GameFi platform, and build a Universal Amusement Park together with global community. Every planet is an independent game genre, which include RPG, Cards, Casual Social Games and so on.
overview.zh: Metasens 是帝國科技集團於 2021 年第四季度推出的元宇宙項目。它旨在提供一個開放的GameFi平台，與全球社區一起建設一個宇宙遊樂園。遊樂園內每個星球都是一個獨立的遊戲類型，包括RPG、卡牌、休閒社交遊戲等。
